Package org.eclipse.persistence.internal.eis.cobol

Class CompositeFieldMetaData

java.lang.Object
org.eclipse.persistence.internal.eis.cobol.ElementaryFieldMetaData
org.eclipse.persistence.internal.eis.cobol.CompositeFieldMetaData
All Implemented Interfaces:
CompositeObject, FieldMetaData
public class CompositeFieldMetaData extends ElementaryFieldMetaData implements CompositeObject
Purpose: This class represents metadata for composite fields. It exetends ElementaryFieldMetaData and adds teh attribute myCompositeFields which is a collection of subordinate fields.
